					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I like this one. It's definitely got it's flaws, and I don't see any conceivable reason why it should be classified as 'Keter,' but I was interested and invested all the way through. If anything, I just wish it were a bit longer and gave us a bit more information.</p> <p>+1 without a doubt.</p> 
				 	]]>
